flowRoot.flowPara: The first time a device is discovered that contains images, the user is asked if they want to import them, using an in-app notification (or a regular notification, if Photos isn't running). The in-app notification should be displayed in Photos while the device is present (irrespective of whether the regular notification has been dismissed).
Placeholder thumbnails are shown for the images, which are filled in as they are imported.
Once a device has been used as an image source, it is scanned for new images if it reappears. Notifications allow new images to be imported.
